speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']
perseus: exterret animum, noctis horrendae sopor.

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

anceps: o* fi_da^ co_nju*nx la^te^a^t h[ae]c u*n(a) e_st sa^lu*s

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']
perseus: O nate, magni certa progenies patris,

speaker: ['#andromacha']

anceps: spe*s u_na^ phry^gi^bu*s u_ni^c(a) a_ffli*ct[ae] do^mu*s

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#andromacha']

speaker: ['#ulixes andromacha']
